BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Category: Events\nInstructor: Claire R.\nIt’s trivia on the wall! Grab your harness and thinking cap!\nA team-based event where you'll rope up\, retrieve trivia questions from the wall\, and work together to lock in answers.\nAll questions are general knowledge\, so you don’t need to be a trivia pro - just come ready to have a great time! The night is hosted by our very own trivia royalty\, Claire\, who’s bringing the questions\, the banter\, and the vibes.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/game-night?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoxNzU1OTA4Mzg=&date=2026-05-27
